<TEXT>
THE CITY state of Bremen confirmed yesterday that a consortium of local
companies had signed a provisional agreement with Klockner-Werke, the
diversified steel group, about the possible purchase of its ailing steel
plant in the region, writes Ariane Genillard in Bonn.
