<HEADLINE>
FT  21 OCT 93 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
GOLD stocks were in focus as the price of bullion climbed above Dollars 370
an ounce. The golds index rose 21, or 1.2 per cent, to 1,771, while
industrials shed 8 to 4,511. The overall index lost 6 to 3,910. De Beers
eased 50 cents to R85.
